  "title": "A Visit from a Friend",
  "summary": "At her home on Residential Avenue in Capital City on Etti IV, the Corporate Sector Authority official Simone Drake answers a knock to find Armstrong, a towering, tattooed Sarian, on her stoop, watched curiously by her dog Duke. Armstrong identifies himself as a fellow Churban sent by Commander Rtufo, then -- as a 'neurapathric' courier -- rolls his eyes back and delivers a message in another man's voice from afar. The sender regrets being unable to speak with Simone before, asks whether she has learned anything more about the whereabouts of someone named Dannan, and offers valuable information that could undermine the stability of Corporate space, which he hopes to see crumble, invoking their shared Churban bond. After the message ends, an intrigued Simone arranges to meet Armstrong later to discuss the matter once she has made her preparations, and he tells her he has rented a room in the city.",
